(FAINT, DISTORTED SPEECH)

23:57.120 --> 23:58.713
Bank robbers. Whatever.

23:58.800 --> 24:01.395
It's got to be ready for an 8:30 start
in the a.m.

24:01.760 --> 24:02.750
(CLEARLY) Questions?

24:04.520 --> 24:05.874
I got a question, Doc.

24:05.960 --> 24:09.556
Why would I believe Phones over here
heard a goddamn word you said?

24:09.640 --> 24:12.439
You laid down your whole play.
He ain't even listening.

24:14.000 --> 24:15.116
Baby?

24:20.880 --> 24:22.030
The target is an armored truck

24:22.120 --> 24:23.839
at Perimeter Trust in Dunwoody,
10:00 a.m. sharp.

24:23.920 --> 24:25.274
We have the details of the route

24:25.400 --> 24:27.631
because someone at the depot
has a nasal problem.

24:27.720 --> 24:29.200
The bank itself
is right near the Buford Highway,

24:29.320 --> 24:31.596
so we should be able to hit the ramp
within 60 seconds of getting out.

24:31.680 --> 24:33.273
We also have a diversion crew.

24:33.360 --> 24:35.272
They're gonna blow up
a bread truck a ways away,

24:35.360 --> 24:36.476
keep the fuzz busy.

24:36.560 --> 24:39.155
The dress code
is the Michael Myers Halloween mask,

24:39.240 --> 24:41.709
but don't all buy your masks
at the same time. It looks suspicious.

24:42.320 --> 24:43.356
The switch car is ready,

24:43.440 --> 24:45.352
but you want me to hit
the long-stay parking structure

24:45.440 --> 24:46.476
at Hartsfield-Jackson

24:46.560 --> 24:48.631
to get a heist vehicle
that stays colder longer.

24:48.720 --> 24:50.598
Boost a commuter car, a family car,

24:50.680 --> 24:52.399
something that blends in well
with morning traffic.

24:53.080 --> 24:56.198
Something on the heavy side
in case we need to ram the cops off the road.

24:56.280 --> 24:58.920
A Escalade, Yukon, Avalanche, whatever.

24:59.320 --> 25:02.518
It needs to be ready
for an 8:30 start in the a.m.

25:04.000 --> 25:05.195
Questions?

25:05.640 --> 25:06.869
Well, ain't y'all cute.

25:06.960 --> 25:08.189
That's my Baby.

25:08.800 --> 25:10.154
Fuck your Baby.

25:34.040 --> 25:35.713
BATS: What's in there is ours.

25:36.040 --> 25:37.633
It belongs to us.

25:38.440 --> 25:41.080
They took our money,
our hard-earned paper.

25:41.160 --> 25:42.435
They snuck in
when we were asleep last night

25:42.560 --> 25:45.314
and took the pants off the chair
and emptied our wallets.

25:46.120 --> 25:48.794
They got what's rightfully ours.

25:49.880 --> 25:51.360
Let's go get it back,

25:51.760 --> 25:53.114
what's rightfully ours.

25:55.000 --> 25:56.992
(NEAT NEAT NEAT BY THE DAMNED PLAYS)

25:57.640 --> 25:59.916
