29:33.200 --> 29:34.270
BATS: Let's rock!

29:35.080 --> 29:36.833
- (ENGINE REVVING)
- (BABY CRYING)

29:37.280 --> 29:38.350
Let's go!

29:39.960 --> 29:43.397
Oh, shit! No! Fuck!

29:45.360 --> 29:46.760
