52:07.920 --> 52:09.036
Yes, you will.

52:09.240 --> 52:11.596
You're not just saying
what you think I want to hear, right?

52:11.680 --> 52:14.149
You consider me a friend, don't you?

52:15.480 --> 52:16.880
You and I are a team.

52:16.960 --> 52:19.270
Nothing is more important
than our friendship.

52:20.040 --> 52:21.269
Good to know.

52:21.600 --> 52:23.557
