53:25.320 --> 53:26.834
You in?

53:27.400 --> 53:28.720
I'm in, Baby.

53:29.560 --> 53:30.755
See you soon.

53:30.840 --> 53:31.990
(DIAL TONE DRONES)

53:39.440 --> 53:40.396
- (ELEVATOR BELL DINGS)
