54:23.640 --> 54:24.676
DARLING: Yeah.

54:26.080 --> 54:27.480
Watch your mouth.

54:27.600 --> 54:29.319
I'll watch what I want to watch.

54:31.000 --> 54:32.195
(BATS SIGHS)

54:34.720 --> 54:36.120
BUDDY: Is that true?

54:36.200 --> 54:38.078
Is that why you have
music in your head all the time?

54:38.160 --> 54:40.356
- Drown out the noise?
- Yeah.

54:40.440 --> 54:41.715
It keeps me moving.

54:42.040 --> 54:44.953
It's an escape. I get it.

54:45.040 --> 54:47.953
Hey, Buddy, you seen a violin?
I had a violin here.

54:48.040 --> 54:49.554
Shut up.

54:51.840 --> 54:53.638
I used to fool around with cars
when I was a kid.

54:53.720 --> 54:56.030
Drive around all night like a speed freak
listening to the radio.

54:57.000 --> 55:02.549
I used to have my special tape that
had my killer track on it. Get me flying.

55:02.640 --> 55:05.280
- You got one of those?
- Sure.

55:06.400 --> 55:07.834
Well, what is it?

55:07.920 --> 55:09.479
- Brighton Rock.
- What?

55:09.560 --> 55:10.676
Queen?

55:11.440 --> 55:13.193
