right through the wall. (SNIFFS)

55:19.560 --> 55:20.630
You got it on here?

55:21.160 --> 55:22.719
Uh, I got it on this one.

55:23.480 --> 55:25.915
Play it. Let's hear that killer track.

55:31.240 --> 55:32.913
(BRIGHTON ROCK INTRO PLAYS)

55:35.280 --> 55:37.112
Yeah.

55:40.280 --> 55:41.760
(ROCK INTRO PLAYS)

