The postal service is dying.

57:18.200 --> 57:20.351
People don't care about their mail anymore.

57:20.440 --> 57:23.956
Lucky for us, their loss is our gain.

57:25.240 --> 57:26.674
Money orders.

57:26.760 --> 57:29.594
For I happen to know a guy
who has a machine

57:29.680 --> 57:32.593
