57:32.680 --> 57:37.914
Each box contains 250 slips per box,
each slip worth up to a grand.

57:38.000 --> 57:39.912
That's quarter a mil per box.

57:40.560 --> 57:42.438
Dot, dot, dot. You do the math.

57:42.560 --> 57:43.994
Darling goes in the front.

57:44.400 --> 57:47.677
Buddy takes a five-alligator count
and follows her inside.

57:47.760 --> 57:52.789
You put on these privacy glasses
to blind the CCTV camera.

57:52.920 --> 57:54.559
Another five-alligator count.

57:54.680 --> 57:57.036
Darling gets in line,
Buddy takes her hostage,

57:57.160 --> 57:58.196
shotgun to her head.

57:58.280 --> 58:00.431
That gets you guys in the back office.

58:01.600 --> 58:03.876
We role-play that a lot.

58:04.120 --> 58:05.190
Uh-huh.

58:05.280 --> 58:07.511
Baby drives Bats around the loading dock.

58:07.640 --> 58:11.554
Bats uses this security card
supplied by an insider with a nasal problem

58:11.680 --> 58:13.751
to get in the staff entrance
and cover the rear.

58:13.880 --> 58:16.315
You guys grab all the boxes
and then sneak out the back

58:16.440 --> 58:18.113
to Baby and the waiting car.

58:21.960 --> 58:23.076
Did you get all that, Baby?

58:23.280 --> 58:24.509
Yeah.

58:24.640 --> 58:25.960
Okay, one more thing.

58:26.280 --> 58:29.956
We need some fresh hardware,
not traceable to us or any previous jobs.

58:30.720 --> 58:33.952
Now, I've got some contacts
who can get us some clean firepower,

58:34.040 --> 58:35.360
so the pickup is tonight.

58:35.440 --> 58:37.750
But after the pickup,
you come straight back here.

58:37.840 --> 58:40.435
You all have an early start in the morning,
and there's eyes everywhere.

58:41.000 --> 58:43.595
So, you're staying the night here.

58:44.920 --> 58:47.116
Oh, we in bed together now.

58:49.800 --> 58:51.678
(INTRO TO NOWHERE TO RUN PLAYING)

58:56.200 --> 58:59.716
- WOMAN: (SINGING) Nowhere to run to, baby
- (SINGING ALONG)

58:59.800 --> 59:02.395
Nowhere to hide

59:03.440 --> 59:07.400
Got nowhere to run to, baby

59:07.520 --> 59:10.115
Nowhere to hide

59:10.760 --> 59:13.753
It's not love I'm a-running from...

59:13.840 --> 59:15.797
Pull over there. I got to take a leak.

59:18.760 --> 59:20.877
BATS: Want some gum?
Want some gum, Buddy?

59:20.960 --> 59:22.553
BUDDY: Yeah, I'll take some gum.

59:23.800 --> 59:25.234
