- Mmm.

59:36.480 --> 59:39.040
You know what was real, real romantic?

59:39.360 --> 59:41.477
What was real, real romantic?

59:42.000 --> 59:43.673
When you stabbed that guy.

59:43.880 --> 59:45.394
(CHUCKLES) Which guy?

59:45.480 --> 59:47.551
The guy that robbed you,
the guy that called you a whore,

59:47.680 --> 59:49.114
