59:49.480 --> 59:50.630
(CHUCKLES) The last one.

59:50.760 --> 59:52.752
Yeah. I do remember that.

59:53.400 --> 59:55.551
Bats just looked at me funny.

59:55.960 --> 59:57.474
(SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE)

59:58.560 --> 01:00:00.279
BUDDY: You want me to kill Bats?

01:00:01.200 --> 01:00:03.431
Not before the job, silly. Hmm?

01:00:05.520 --> 01:00:07.477
You think we should talk about this
in front of Baby?

01:00:07.560 --> 01:00:11.440
- (DOOR OPENS, BELL CHIMES)
- He won't say a thing. Will you, Baby? Hmm?

01:00:14.520 --> 01:00:15.636
Jesus Christ.

01:00:16.160 --> 01:00:17.310
What, did you steal all this?

01:00:17.480 --> 01:00:18.880
You said you wanted some gum.

01:00:18.960 --> 01:00:21.680
Fuck I'm supposed to do, pay for it?
Let's go.

01:00:23.440 --> 01:00:24.510
- Let's go.
- (REVVING ENGINE)

01:00:26.800 --> 01:00:28.837
I can't around it, no

01:00:28.920 --> 01:00:30.752
Nowhere to run

01:00:30.840 --> 01:00:33.594
Nowhere to hide from you, baby...

