BATS: Looks like
the farmers' market is open.

01:00:35.720 --> 01:00:36.949
DARLING: Farmers' market?

01:00:37.080 --> 01:00:39.879
BUDDY: Yeah. Doc says
we got to go see The Butcher.

01:01:09.400 --> 01:01:10.914
(WHISTLING A MELODY)

01:01:16.760 --> 01:01:18.479
Come on, you're going in with us.

01:01:18.960 --> 01:01:20.792
